HAPPENING TODAY ‼️

Ugadi Subhakankshalu in advance! Come join us! Indulge in Ugadi Pachadi and Mango Lassi, get lovely Henna designs, and so much more! 🧡

7:30 pm to 8:30 pm at the Fireside Lounge, Center for Spiritual and Religious Life - We hope to see you there!

Spring into new beginnings this Ugadi, the Hindu New Year! Embark on a festive journey with a spoonful of Ugadi Pachadi, laughter-filled games, and the warmth of new friends!

Event is open to all. We hope to see you there! ✨

#ugadi #hindyyuva #vanderbiltuniversity

Hindu YUVA is now at Vanderbilt University!

Hindu YUVA aims to provide a platform to preserve, practice, promote, and protect Hindu Dharma by bringing together Hindu youth across America. Hindu YUVA creates opportunities for college communities (students, staff, and faculty members) to understand and practice Hindu Dharma or the Hindu way of life.

Feel free to reach out to us to know more and join our community!
